com.maxleap

类 MLGeoPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.maxleap.MLGeoPoint

  • public class MLGeoPoint
extends Object
    MLGeoPoint represents a latitude / longitude point that may be associated with a key in a MLObject or used as a reference point for geo queries. This allows proximity based queries on the key.

    • 构造器概要

      构造器 
      构造器和说明
      MLGeoPoint()
      Creates a new default point with latitude and longitude set to 0.0.
      MLGeoPoint(double latitude, double longitude)
      Creates a new point with the specified latitude and longitude.
